  "remarks": "\nAli Reza KHANCHI is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: Ali Reza KHANCHI is or has been responsible for engaging in, providing support for and facilitating a relevant nuclear activity in, or for use in, Iran. \n",
